FuncDef: This command renumbers existing IP(IPv4), IPv6, or MAC filter entries to re-sequence filter entries.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies the entry number of an existing entry. Values-1 to 6144 for ip-filter and ipv6-filter.
Specifies the new entry number to be assigned to the old entry. Values-1 to 6144 for ip-filter and ipv6-filter.
